Barry Nelson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barry_Nelson 0 Barry Nelson (born Haakon Robert Nielsen, April 16, 1917 – April 7, 2007) was an American actor, noted as the first actor to portray Ian Fleming's secret agent James Bond.
